TITLE: Describing XPath Query Operators - XPath
DESCRIPTION: This snippet lists various XPath operators that can be applied in query constraints for Mendix applications, detailing their uses and expected return values. Key parameters include operators like '=', '!=', '<', '>', and logical operators 'and', 'or'. Expected inputs are price comparisons, and outputs are boolean values indicating the result of the comparisons.
