TITLE: Asynchronous Delay Function with Promise
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of an asynchronous wait function using Promise and setTimeout to create a delay in execution.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mendix/docs/blob/development/content/en/docs/howto9/extensibility/best-practices-javascript-actions.md#2025-04-21_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function Wait(delay) {
    // BEGIN USER CODE
    return new Promise(function(resolve) {
        window.setTimeout(function(){
            resolve();
        }, delay);
    });
    // END USER CODE
}
```

