TITLE: Adding Custom Validation Logic in TextBox Component - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to implement a custom validation method in the TextBox component, which checks if the requiredMessage property is populated and if the input value is present. Validation messages are applied as necessary.
