TITLE: Platform-Specific Styling for GroupBox Widget
DESCRIPTION: Updated styling that introduces platform-specific border radius adjustments. iOS devices will have rounded corners with a 4px radius, while Android devices will have square corners.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mendix/docs/blob/development/content/en/docs/howto/extensibility/build-native-widget.md#2025-04-21_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
const defaultStyle: CustomStyle = {
    container: {
        borderColor: "#000000",
