TITLE: Installing Mendix Pipelines Using Helm
DESCRIPTION: Helm command to install Mendix pipelines in the air-gapped environment, specifying the necessary images and repositories.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mendix/docs/blob/development/content/en/docs/deployment/private-cloud/private-cloud-tekton/private-cloud-tekton-airgap.md#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
cd $PATH_TO_DOWNLOADED_FOLDERS && cd helm/charts
helm install -n $NAMESPACE_WITH_PIPELINES mx-tekton-pipeline ./pipeline/ \
  -f ./pipeline/values.yaml \
