LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
FROM
	{
		entity_name | ( sub_oql_query )
	}
	[ [ AS ] from_alias ]

	{
		{ INNER | { { LEFT | RIGHT | FULL } [ OUTER ] } } JOIN
		entity_path [ [ AS ] from_alias ]
		[ ON <constraint> ]
	} [ ,...n ]
```

