SOURCE: https://github.com/mendix/docs/blob/development/content/en/docs/apidocs-mxsdk/apidocs/studio-pro/extensibility-api/csharp/extensibility-api-howtos/build-todo-example-extension.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

