TITLE: Indenting with Tabs and a Line Break – DO NOT USE TABS Markdown
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the pitfalls of using tabs along with line breaks in Markdown list items. It highlights that while tabs may appear to work for generic list items, they can break the formatting of more complex elements like code blocks.
