TITLE: Implementing Message Handling in JavaScript for Mendix Extension
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript code sets up message handling for communication between the web view and the extension logic. It defines a helper function for posting messages and registers a message listener.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mendix/docs/blob/development/content/en/docs/apidocs-mxsdk/apidocs/studio-pro/extensibility-api/csharp/extensibility-api-howtos/build-todo-example-extension.md#2025-04-21_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function postMessage(message, data) {
  window.chrome.webview.postMessage({ message, data });
}

// Register message handler.
window.chrome.webview.addEventListener("message", handleMessage);
// Indicate that you are ready to receive messages.
