TITLE: Querying Customers by City in SQL
DESCRIPTION: This SQL query fetches the first names of customers who reside in 'Rotterdam'. It demonstrates the use of INNER JOIN to combine tables and apply conditions on the joined tables. It works with tables Sales.Customer and Sales.Address and includes a condition based on the City field.
