LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT COUNT(*) AS LocationCount, SUM(Stock) as CityStock, City AS City
FROM Sales.Location AS Location
GROUP BY City
HAVING
	SUM(Stock) <= (
		SELECT COUNT(*)
		FROM Sales.Location
	)
```

